{"tid":2177984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地對美審計要求讓步","createTime":"2020-08-28T05:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T06:40:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6d9ecd7501b9628ea9f00fa3bc91dbd2f2a8f7","tid":2177984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200828/63VT44QYEVDH5AQJ4HC62AIQ6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200828%2F63VT44QYEVDH5AQJ4HC62AIQ6I%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=aac257f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200828%2F63VT44QYEVDH5AQJ4HC62AIQ6I%2F&h=1af0d9bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200828/63VT44QYEVDH5AQJ4HC62AIQ6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內地對美審計要求讓步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n■中證監向美國上市公司會計監督委員會（PCAOB）提出新建議，美國可以挑選任何一間中國國企，進行中美聯合跨境審計測試。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美針鋒相對，赴美上市的中概股成美國打壓對象。中國證監會副主席方星海於訪問稱，中國公司跨境審議爭拗問題，中方有讓步；中證監向美國上市公司會計監督委員會（PCAOB）提出新建議，美國可以挑選任何一間中國國企，進行中美聯合跨境審計測試。<br />\n<br />\n56歲方星海周三接受彭博訪問透露，中證監本月初向PCAOB發出建議書，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敏感資料以節錄提交<br />\n<br />\n不過中方也設立條件，就是中方以國家安全為由，並按國際慣例，把部份中國國企審計底稿的敏感資料，以節錄形式提交。<br />\n<br />\n方星海續指，中證監今年4月曾建議以中國私人企業，作為中美聯合審計測。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n方星海表示，試過邀請美方進行視像或電話會議，惟未獲回應。至於中美聯合。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6b92e49983d41bd06a5c18ab97012308e5eb4088","tid":2177984,"uid":269481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦，物又係老作，audit黎有咩意義？<br />\n<br />\n快啲踢走晒呢啲垃圾公司啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fe65d290014bf43c84e9688d90a9e32606852b","tid":2177984,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"中國擺明拖時間，如果美國人相信就真係智力有問題。"},{"pid":"b26921e97137d78b40cfd9c7610e28b43621c93e","tid":2177984,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"經中国手的audit還算是audit嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edd6d8f4595d949bc1ab7b5d1fbdcdf928dd61f","tid":2177984,"uid":28913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"正常公司: 你要咩我拎比你睇<br />\n中國公司: 你要咩我造比你睇"},{"pid":"502f541c751d03f710837088f7df8c0f43885613","tid":2177984,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0edd6d8f4595d949bc1ab7b5d1fbdcdf928dd61f","tid":2177984,"uid":28913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"正常公司: 你要咩我拎比你睇<br />\n中國公司: 你要咩我造比你睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">把部份中國國企審計底稿的敏感資料，以節錄形式提交</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0197f0a1de0d3b4f8dea3ebcb3fda2fb39ac414a","tid":2177984,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"外國政府唔會幫公司做假數<br />\n支那就政府 銀行 公司高層一齊合作呃錢<br />\n<br />\n拒絕中資短期內會搵少咗錢<br />\n不過長遠對美國股市健康同埋美國人有更好嘅保障"},{"pid":"37ea5c09f71b41a70d949c9f4293bd839b52b359","tid":2177984,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"我估最終美國都讓步"},{"pid":"42daf21c74bd0d03d158d0323435e181a15a5434","tid":2177984,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"睇左內地對審美要求讓步<br />\n心諗咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d98d2459c5287995668debc3d22e931e8f998ee","tid":2177984,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"急了<br />\n再集唔到美金就斷資金鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6816971905806e97fe05d17f63f3b60e2e8b2be1","tid":2177984,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike